wdi-GC.XPN.COMP.CN.def: Compensation of employees consists of all payments in cash, as well as in kind (such as food and housing), to employees in return for services rendered, and government contributions to social insurance schemes such as social security and pensions that provide benefits to employees.
wdi-GC.XPN.COMP.CN.name: Compensation of employees
wdi-GC.XPN.COMP.CN.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.
